# Phase 3.5 qlib data (gitignored; ~1.5 GB binary OHLCV for ~5500 A-shares
# 1990-now). Stored at the qlib-standard path — overrideable via
# QLIB_CN_DATA_PATH env var for users who keep data on a separate volume.
.qlib/
qlib_data/
# Skipped-ticker manifest from ingest — informational, not under source control.
qlib_skipped.txt
# Safety net: vendored collectors default their working dirs to CUR_DIR when
# invoked directly. Our qlib_ingest wrappers redirect these to ~/.cache, but
# ignore any that still land under the vendored tree so they never get committed.
mosaic/dataflows/collectors/**/source/
mosaic/dataflows/collectors/**/normalize/
mosaic/dataflows/collectors/**/tmp/
results/
logs/

